msgctxt "84_Businessman"
msgid "Did you hear? A kidnapper took a little boy as a hostage and is using him as a shield on that roof over there!"
msgstr "¿Escuchaste? ¡Un secuestrador agarro a un niño y lo está usando de escudo humano en los tejados!"

msgctxt "96_Businessman"
msgid "I saw a woman detective chasing after them, though. Hope everything is all right..."
msgstr "I saw a woman detective chasing after them, though. Hope everything is all right..."

msgctxt "108_Kiryu"
msgid "(A kidnapping, huh? That's no joke. It would be best to stay out of this, but it may be a chance to have a <Color:7>Revelation<Color:Default>...)"
msgstr "(A kidnapping, huh? That's no joke. It would be best to stay out of this, but it may be a chance to have a <Color:7>Revelation<Color:Default>...)"

msgctxt "120_Akiyama"
msgid "(Even a detective might have trouble if she's all alone. This is a rare type of case. Perhaps this will give me a <Color:7>Revelation<Color:Default>...)"
msgstr "(Even a detective might have trouble if she's all alone. This is a rare type of case. Perhaps this will give me a <Color:7>Revelation<Color:Default>...)"

